data.description: Maintenance free 3 bedroom 2.5 bath 2 story complete with main floor master! When entering you are greeted by a foyer that transitions to the beautiful open concept great room & then into the heart of this home - the kitchen. Gorgeous granite countertops & a large center island, perfect for entertaining guests! The large master suite includes your own bath featuring a custom design tiled shower, separate soaking tub, double vanity sinks & a LARGE walk-in closet. The main floor is complete with the finished laundry room & half bath connecting to the heated two-car garage. Upstairs you will find 2 oversized bedrooms & a large hallway bathroom! The basement provides additional storage or living space to complete the layout! Finally enjoy your morning coffee on the large patio in the privately fenced back yard. Home is also equipped with a whole house generator!
